Interactable Role

Serious

Interactive UI elements (e.g. button, link, inputs etc.), must express their semantics by their type (classes, traits, and relevant accessibility services), so that screen readers and other assistive technologies can read it correctly and so that the user can accurately predict the result of interacting with it.

  • Class Name: android.widget.TextView

Color Contrast

Serious

Ensures the contrast between foreground and background colors meets WCAG 2 AA contrast ratio thresholds. The minimum contrast ratio is 4.5:1 for font sizes less than 24dp and 3:1 for font sizes 24dp or higher.
